The paper discusses the development of scene-aware dialog systems using state-of-the-art technologies from multiple research areas, including end-to-end dialog technologies, visual question answering (VQA) technologies, and video description technologies. These areas are all related to computer vision, natural language processing, and machine learning, which are covered by the arXiv CS sub-categories cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, and cs.MM. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
